data.description: The Firestone Plus Plan by local builder Tindall Construction. Two story grand staircase and dining area greets you upon entering this 6 bedroom, 3.5 bath home. Main living space is open concept and gracious two-story great room. Owner's suite is on the main has an amazing bathroom and divided closet. Five generous bedrooms upstairs. Huge 25' x 25' garage easily fits a full sized truck or large SUV plus built in work bench and additional 3rd bay. Home will include LifeProof Luxury Vinyl waterproof wood plank floors, granite counter tops, accent lighting, laundry chute, radiant barrier roof sheathing, full landscape and irrigation, CAT 5/6 fiber cable, and plenty of storage space in this 3025sf home. Home comes with Quality Home Builders 2-10 warranty. To be completed by end of July.  Large flat lots convenient to Ft. Gordon, Shopping, Dining, I-20 & I-520!
